{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/remote-dev-tailscale-mosh-tmux-happy/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"RUN:DEVEL:RUN"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ace4c267-7850-5671-b3f3-cfc9ba089d64","excerpt":"☀️ 환경 Rocky Linux 10.1 iPhone / iPad (Termius, Happy Coder 앱) ✋ 들어가며 아이패드로 개발이 되냐고? 된다. 스마트폰으로도 된다. 모든 부담은 서버에서 가져가고 아이패드는 그냥 아이패드다. 서버만 켜져 있으면 된다. 음성 입력까지 지원하니 스마트폰 들고 \"이 버그 고쳐라\" 한 마디로도 충분하다. 필자가 직접 …","html":"<h2 id=\"️-환경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"️ 환경 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>☀️ 환경</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Rocky Linux 10.1</li>\n<li>iPhone / iPad (Termius, Happy Coder 앱)</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"-들어가며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\" 들어가며 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>✋ 들어가며</h2>\n<p>아이패드로 개발이 되냐고? 된다. 스마트폰으로도 된다.</p>\n<p>모든 부담은 서버에서 가져가고 아이패드는 그냥 아이패드다.</p>\n<p>서버만 켜져 있으면 된다. 음성 입력까지 지원하니 스마트폰 들고 \"이 버그 고쳐라\" 한 마디로도 충분하다.</p>\n<p>필자가 직접 사용하고 있는 Tailscale + Mosh + Tmux + Happy Coder 조합의 세팅을 정리했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"-Tailscale\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-Tailscale\" aria-label=\" Tailscale permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>🌐 Tailscale</h2>\n<p>WireGuard 기반 메시 VPN. 포트포워딩 없이 서버에 <code class=\"language-text\">100.x.x.x</code> 고정 IP가 생긴다.</p>\n<p>홈 서버를 외부에서 접속하려면 복잡한 공유기 설정을 거쳐야 한다.</p>\n<p>Tailscale은 그 과정 없이 기기끼리 직접 연결된다. 같은 계정으로 로그인한 기기들이 하나의 가상 네트워크에 묶이는 방식이다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"서버-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"서버 설치 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>서버 설치</em></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-fsSL</span> https://tailscale.com/install.sh <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sh</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> systemctl <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">enable</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--now</span> tailscaled\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> tailscale up</code></pre></div>\n<p>iOS/Android 앱 설치 후 같은 계정으로 로그인하면 끝.</p>\n<h2 id=\"-Mosh\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-Mosh\" aria-label=\" Mosh permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>🔗 Mosh</h2>\n<p>SSH는 와이파이가 바뀌거나 화면이 꺼지면 세션이 죽는다.</p>\n<p>Mosh는 UDP 기반이라 네트워크가 끊겼다 복구돼도 세션이 그대로다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"서버-설치-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-1\" aria-label=\"서버 설치 1 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>서버 설치</em></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> dnf <span class=\"token function\">install</span> mosh\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> firewall-cmd <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--permanent</span> --add-port<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">60000</span>-61000/udp\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> firewall-cmd <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--reload</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Termius 앱 호스트 설정에서 Connection Type을 Mosh로 변경하고 Tailscale IP와 계정 정보를 입력하면 된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"-Tmux\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-Tmux\" aria-label=\" Tmux permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>📺 Tmux</h2>\n<p>Mosh를 끊어도 서버의 Tmux 세션은 살아있다. 이게 핵심이다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"서버-설치-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-2\" aria-label=\"서버 설치 2 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>서버 설치</em></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> dnf <span class=\"token function\">install</span> tmux</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"기본-사용법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"기본 사용법 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>기본 사용법</em></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tmux new <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-s</span> dev      <span class=\"token comment\"># 'dev' 이름의 세션 시작</span>\nCtrl+b, d            <span class=\"token comment\"># 세션에서 나가기 (서버에서는 계속 실행됨)</span>\ntmux attach <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-t</span> dev   <span class=\"token comment\"># 'dev' 세션에 다시 접속</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"-Happy-Coder\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-Happy-Coder\" aria-label=\" Happy Coder permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>🤖 Happy Coder</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/slopus/happy\">Happy Coder</a>는 Claude Code를 모바일에서 제어할 수 있는 오픈소스 클라이언트다.</p>\n<p>터미널, iOS, Android, 웹 앱 전부 실시간으로 동기화된다.</p>\n<p>Claude Code가 입력을 기다리거나 작업이 완료되면 푸시 알림이 오고, End-to-End 암호화로 코드와 대화 내용이 보호된다.</p>\n<p>서버의 Tmux 세션에서 <code class=\"language-text\">claude</code> 대신 <code class=\"language-text\">happy</code>를 실행해두면 아이폰/아이패드/안드로이드 앱 혹은 웹브라우저에서 제어할 수 있다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"서버-설치-3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-3\" aria-label=\"서버 설치 3 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>서버 설치</em></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-g</span> happy-coder</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"사용법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"사용법 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>사용법</em></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">happy  <span class=\"token comment\"># claude 대신 실행</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"사용-시나리오\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EC%8B%9C%EB%82%98%EB%A6%AC%EC%98%A4\" aria-label=\"사용 시나리오 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>사용 시나리오</em></strong></h4>\n<ol>\n<li>서버 Tmux 세션에서 <code class=\"language-text\">happy</code> 실행</li>\n<li>아이폰/아이패드 Happy 앱에서 작업 지시</li>\n<li>작업 완료되거나 Claude Code가 질문이 생기면 앱으로 푸시 알림</li>\n<li>앱에서 바로 응답하면 작업 재개</li>\n</ol>\n<p>앱에서 음성 입력도 지원해서 꼭 아이패드일 필요도 없다. 스마트폰을 들고 \"이 버그 고쳐라\" 한 마디면 끝이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\" permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>👋</h2>\n<p>Tailscale로 어디서든 접속하고, Mosh로 연결을 유지하고, Tmux로 세션을 보존하고, Happy Coder로 AI까지 붙였다.</p>\n<p>그리고 이 모든 게 전부 무료다. <del>클로드 빼고 ㅎㅎ</del></p>\n<p>아이패드는 그냥 우리가 알던 아이패드다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"아이패드(혹은 스마트폰)로 원격 개발하기 — Tailscale + Mosh + Tmux + Happy Coder","date":"March 12, 2026","update":"March 12, 2026","tags":["tailscale","mosh","tmux","rocky-linux","ipad","iphone","remote-development","termius","happy-coder","claude-code"],"series":null,"emoji":"📱"},"fields":{"slug":"/remote-dev-tailscale-mosh-tmux-happy/","readingTime":{"minutes":4.05}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"f527215b-b4a1-56f7-b568-44e14e80390d","fields":{"slug":"/intellij-vo-mybatis-xml/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"VO 및 Mybatis XML 자동 생성하기 (with. IntelliJ)","emoji":"🚘"}}},{"node":{"id":"b959a78f-45a4-5cae-89ec-75ce63644e15","fields":{"slug":"/linux-swap-memory/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"리눅스 Swap memory 할당/해제","emoji":"💿"}}},{"node